The employer may deduct a processing fee from the remainder of the debtor's earnings, even if the remainder would be exempt under RCW
74.20A.090
. The processing fee shall not exceed fifteen dollars from the first disbursement to the department and one dollar for each subsequent disbursement under the assignment of earnings.
